        <mxCell id="Ly3KYa2bKOGt5wKo04HH-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="130" x="20" y="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Ly3KYa2bKOGt5wKo04HH-89" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-202&quot;&gt;1. User Management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-202&quot;&gt;: Clients must be able to create accounts, log in, and manage subscription plans (inherited from Experiment 4).&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0,1,1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-202 citation-end-202&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-202&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,1,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3,1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-201 interactive-span-hovered&quot;&gt;2. Adaptive Video Streaming&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-201 interactive-span-hovered&quot;&gt;: Clients should be able to watch videos with zero or negligible buffering across multiple resolutions (480p, 720p, 1080p, 4K)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,1,1,1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-201 citation-end-201 interactive-span-hovered&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,1,1,2&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-202&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,1,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;3. Manifest Utilization&lt;/b&gt;: The system must use &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;42&quot;&gt;Manifest Files&lt;/b&gt; (.m3u8 for HLS or .mpd for DASH) to guide the client player through various video segments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-202&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;3,1,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;4. Engagement Handling&lt;/b&gt;: Users can &quot;Like&quot; and &quot;Comment&quot; on videos. This must be handled synchronously without a Pub-Sub model to ensure immediate interaction feedback at scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="570" x="20" y="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Ly3KYa2bKOGt5wKo04HH-90" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="170" x="10" y="190" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Ly3KYa2bKOGt5wKo04HH-91" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-200&quot;&gt;Scalability&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-200&quot;&gt;: The system must support &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;37&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-200&quot;&gt;200-300 million users&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-200&quot;&gt; and roughly 20,000 hours of content&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,1,1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-200 citation-end-200&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,1,2&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,1,2&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,1,0&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-199&quot;&gt;CAP Theorem Priority&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-199&quot;&gt;: The system prioritizes &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;45&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-199&quot;&gt;Availability over Consistency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-199&quot;&gt; for video playback, but requires &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;108&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-199&quot;&gt;Strict Consistency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-199&quot;&gt; for payments and subscriptions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,1,1&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-199 citation-end-199&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,1,2&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,1,2&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,1,0&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-198&quot;&gt;Low Latency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-198&quot;&gt;: System response time should ideally stay within &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;61&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-198&quot;&gt;50 - 80 ms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,1,1&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-198 citation-end-198&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,1,2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,1,2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;High Concurrency for Engagement&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;: Likes and comments must be processed efficiently at peak loads without a messaging queue (no Pub-Sub).&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="610" x="20" y="220" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Ly3KYa2bKOGt5wKo04HH-93" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Core Entities&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
